QuestData.Title: Maw Manifested
QuestData.Description:
Ya heard it from Mueh'zala himself... tanks to ol' Bwonsamdi. Dere be an ancient spirit trapped in da Maw. Me bettin' da Winter Queen gonna want it back.
Good ting ya been goin' down dere yaself, hm? Should be nice an' easy for ya.
Me gonna clean up da rest of da undead here. Meet ol' Bwonsamdi in Ardenweald when ya get back.
QuestData.LogDescription: Travel to the Maw to find the lost wild god of Ardenweald.
QuestData.RewardText:
All me trainin' as a shadow hunter been leadin' ta dis moment.
Trackin' a spirit inside da Maw and savin' dem from eternal torture...
